name: S A K U R A
description: A symbolic flower of the spring, a time of renewal, and the fleeting nature of life. Their life is very short. After their beauty peaks around two weeks, the blossoms start to fall. ... Hanami literally means “watching blossoms,” and the tradition can be traced back at least a thousand years. It combines with black and white photography and characteristic Far East font and turns into a unique nft. Lo-fi sounds...
